SETTING THE FONT SIZE
It should only be set once: In the body tag with 16px - everything else should be done with ems
Then the golden ratio should be used.

Use percentages for containers and semantic tags

Use script to brink IE to this century.


Responsive design: 
Use meta tag in addition to the media queries.
Add more padding around buttons in the mobile css so it's possible to tab it with the fingers